data.text: @madison_dobbs I’d agree with that. It only furthers partisanship because people aren’t willing to fact check with other news outlets. Also, most people aren’t willing to admit that both sides do some good things and some bad things

@AndrewSWHarper oh it definitely goes both ways. you're gonna be hard pressed to find a news outlet that isn't obviously biased one way or another. the issue is people not realizing this and taking everything one news outlet says as fact, which sadly is often the case
